# Rust
/target
**/target
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Node / web / desktop frontend
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/out

# Local data, secrets, env
**/.data
.env
**/.env
**/.env*.local

# Updater signing keys — the private key is kept outside the repo (see RELEASING.md);
# this is a belt-and-suspenders guard so a key can never be committed by accident.
*.key
!**/*.key.pub
.tauri/

# Lectern-generated native skills (materialized from the skills DB on each run)
**/.claude/skills/lectern-*

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
.idea
.vscode

# Session/tooling artifacts (G6 hygiene)
graphify-out/
.graphifyignore
MEMORY.md.tmp
skills-lock.json

# Local tooling / agent instructions — not part of the product, keep out of git.
.agent/
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
MEMORY.md

# apps/web lives in the separate lectern-web repo; keep any stray generated files out.
apps/web/
